KPG/Kw's webPage Generator. The smaller brother of KWD.
==============

PURPOSE
==============
Generating HTML. With help of Markdown, which is awesome.

INSTALLATION
==============
Edit the kpgtemplate.html.

USAGE
==============
./kpg /location/of/markdowned/file - the first line must be the title of your content, the second line shall be the H1 line.

